snippet.textDisplay:
Pro+ & XS Max series names are just getting out of control & dare say.....”stupid” 🤔
Know that the “Pro”, “Gamer”, etc....buzz words are marketing PR to get sales up; but it’s just creating a naming scheme stack that’s just plain confusing. This just isn’t for the iPhones, iPads, etc...; but also applies to computers, GPUs, CPUs, & basically anything the has a micro chip in it. Even buying a TV or cordless brushless impact driver from various companies, has the consumer dealing w/ a model & naming skew that’s ridiculous.
Kinda miss the days when a company had the next generation’s name a “2”, “3”, “4”, etc...w/o the Plus, Max, XS Max, & everyone’s favorite...”PRO” names😉
